        'The water production rate reaches the highest level specified in the national standard, and adopts more advanced reverse osmosis membrane and design scheme, with higher filtration efficiency and usage performance. For every 100 liters of raw water filtered, at least 60 liters can be used as pure water, with less waste water and higher water utilization.',
