          'Multi-stage filtration purifies the water layer by layer, ensuring the removal of various harmful substances in the water. Front folded pp cartridge and front Jacoby activated carbon share the burden of filtration and extend the service life of reverse osmosis membrane. The rear acid-washed Jacoby activated carbon cartridge further optimizes the taste of the water.',
        icon: 'tabler:adjustments-horizontal',
      },
      {
        title: 'Constant pressure and steady current',
