        icon: 'tabler:plug-connected',
      },
      {
        title: 'Easy to install',
        description:
          'The main body of the water purifier is designed as an integrated structure, which reduces the number of external piping connections and makes installation neater. With the use of quick couplings, piping installation as well as cartridge replacement is simply inserted without the use of special tools or specialized knowledge. Through the video guide, girls can also install on their own.',
        icon: 'tabler:plug-connected',
      },
      {
        title: 'Space-saving',
        description: 
          'Ideal for installation under the kitchen sink or on the countertop, it takes up minimal space. The water purifier body integrates all filtration modules and piping, reducing the size of external connections and add-ons and maximizing space savings in the home or office.',
