          'No electricity, no pump with precision mechanical principles to achieve no noise or very low noise operation state, to provide users with a quieter, more comfortable use of the experience.',
        icon: 'tabler:arrows-right-left',
      },
      {
        title: 'High volume',
        description:
          'Low-pressure osmosis, 150-gallon reverse osmosis membrane achieves an electrified 800-gallon water output, with an average flow rate of up to 2.5 L per minute.Compared to ordinary water purifiers, the volume of water provided by the ultra-high-flow water purifier greatly shortens the waiting time for environments that require quick access to drinking or culinary water.',
